      *
      ** Securities Screen 3 details from incoming transaction
      ** - screen format
     D NwSE3ScnFmt   E DS                  EXTNAME(SESEC3PD)
      *
      ** Securities for file update - file format
     D NwSEFilFmt    E DS                  EXTNAME(SEVSECSPD)
      *
      ** Securities Screen 3 error indicators
     D SEESEC3       E DS                  EXTNAME(SEESEC3PD)
      *
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Declared variables                   ¦
      ** ¦ ==================                   ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Index for arrays of error message ids, etc.
     D IDx             S              3P 0
      *
      ** Parameters for module ZALIGN
     D ZFIELD          S             16A
     D ZADEC           S              1P 0
     D ZADIG           S              2P 0
     D ZALIGNok        S              1A
      *
      ** Work variables for Management fees due/received
     D WMgFeeD         S             11P 0
     D WMgFeeR         S             11P 0
      *
      ** No. of decimal places for Fee currency
     D PFNBDP          S              1P 0
                                                                                            MD000091
      **                                                                                    MD000091
     D BChar           DS                                                                   MD000091
     D   BLen                  1      2B 0                                                  MD000091
     D   LenStr                1      2                                                     MD000091
     D   MsgDtaTmp                   99                                                     MD000091
