      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** +--- Start of Main processing -------------------------------+
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** ¦ *INZSR is executed at program activation.                  ¦
      ** ¦                                                            ¦
      ** +------------------------------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Initialise work variables.
      *
     C                   EVAL      Idx = 0
     C                   Z-ADD     *ZEROS        WMgFeeD
     C                   Z-ADD     *ZEROS        WMgFeeR
      *
      ** Validate management fees due and management fees received.
      *
     C                   EXSR      SRValMFeeDRc
      *
      ** If an error has been found, set return code appropriately.
      ** Otherwise, update valid file fields.
      *
     C                   IF        OKMGFD = 'N' or
     C                             OKMGRC = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn = 'ERROR'
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   IF        OKMGFD <> 'N'
     C                   Z-ADD     WMgFeeD       S1MGFD
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   IF        OKMGRC <> 'N'
     C                   Z-ADD     WMgFeeR       S1MGRC
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   RETURN

      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRValMFeeDRc - Validation for Management Fees Due and        *
      *                 Management Fees Received                      *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************

     C     SRValMFeeDRc  BEGSR
      *
      ** Validation for management fees due.
      *
     C                   IF        DDMGFD <> *BLANKS

     C                   MOVE      *BLANKS       ZFIELD
     C                   MOVEL     DDMGFD        ZFIELD
     C     11            SUB       PFNBDP        ZADIG
     C                   Z-ADD     PFNBDP        ZADEC

     C                   CALLB     'ZALIGN'
     C                   PARM                    ZALIGNok
     C                   PARM                    ZFIELD
     C                   PARM                    ZADEC
     C                   PARM                    ZADIG

     C                   IF        ZALIGNok = 'N'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKMGFD
     C                   ADD       1             Idx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDMGFD'      FldNamXAr(Idx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0105'     MsgIdXAr(Idx)
     C**********         EVAL      MsgDtaXAr(Idx) = 'Management Fees +                      MD000091
     C**********                                    Due'                                    MD000091
     C                   EVAL      MsgDtaTmp = 'Management Fees Due'                        MD000091
     C                   EVAL      BLen = %Len(%Trim(MsgDtaTmp))                            MD000091
     C                   EVAL      MsgDtaXAr(Idx) = LenStr + %TRIM(MsgDtaTmp)               MD000091

     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVE      ZFIELD        WMgFeeD
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** Validation for management fees received.
      *
     C                   IF        DDMGRC <> *BLANKS

     C                   MOVE      *BLANKS       ZFIELD
     C                   MOVEL     DDMGRC        ZFIELD
     C     11            SUB       PFNBDP        ZADIG
     C                   Z-ADD     PFNBDP        ZADEC

     C                   CALLB     'ZALIGN'
     C                   PARM                    ZALIGNok
     C                   PARM                    ZFIELD
     C                   PARM                    ZADEC
     C                   PARM                    ZADIG

     C                   IF        ZALIGNok = 'N'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKMGRC
     C                   ADD       1             Idx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDMGRC'      FldNamXAr(Idx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0105'     MsgIdXAr(Idx)
     C**********         EVAL      MsgDtaXAr(Idx) = 'Management Fees +                      MD000091
     C**********                                    Received'                               MD000091
     C                   EVAL      MsgDtaTmp = 'Management Fees Received'                   MD000091
     C                   EVAL      BLen = %Len(%Trim(MsgDtaTmp))                            MD000091
     C                   EVAL      MsgDtaXAr(Idx) = LenStr + %TRIM(MsgDtaTmp)               MD000091

     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVE      ZFIELD        WMgFeeR
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDIF

     C                   ENDSR

      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Program Initialisation                              *
      *         - This subroutine runs automatically for program      *
      *           initialisation.                                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************

     C     *INZSR        BEGSR

     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
      *
      ** INPUT
      ** =====
      *
      ** Return code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
      *
      ** Securities Screen 3 details from incoming transaction
      ** - screen format
     C                   PARM                    NwSE3ScnFmt
      *
      ** Number of decimal places of fee currency
     C                   PARM                    PFNBDP
      *
      ** OUTPUT
      ** ======
      *
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Securities Screen 3 error indicators
     C                   PARM                    SEESEC3
      *
      ** Securities for file update - file format
     C                   PARM                    NwSEFilFmt
      *
      *
      ** Program, module and procedure names for dbase error processing
      ** ==============================================================
      ** The following /COPY sets these values.
      *
      /COPY ZACPYSRC,DBFIELDS

     C                   ENDSR

